extendedInfo.description: The Image GPS Extractor allows you to take or select an image and extract the GPS Lat/Long coordinates (if any exist).  You can then map the coordinates to Google Maps with the press of a button.  App created to go along with Tutorial at:   http://www.zombieflambe.com/blog/image-gps-extractor/

reviews.title: Didnt work at all
reviews.comment: Picked diff pics from diff cameras and locations. Some it said no data found, but majority went back to coordinate windows but it never displayed gps
reviews.author: A Google User
